info.description: Rich choco cake tucked between layers of silky butterscotch mousse. Irresistible to say the least!

info.name: Fine Chocolate Silk [SWISS]
info.description: Made from the finest cocoa beans from Switzerland, you'll love this chocolaty ice cream adventure.

info.name: Choco-Cookies & Cr?me [NEW YORK]
info.description: Delicious chocolate cookie crumble swirled with real vanilla cream, this extravagant ice cream will take you all the way to New York.

info.description: Made of 100% real vanilla beans from the glorious France! We bet you'll forget the vanilla essenced ice creams after this.

info.description: World's best coffee beans from Colombia & a twist of gooey Chocolate cookies. This ice cream has it all to entice your taste buds!

info.name: Chocolate Brownie Fudge [DUTCH]
info.description: Dense Dutch chocolate fudge with delectable brownie chunks. This ice cream is a treasure for chocolate lovers.

info.description: Created with forest berries from California, this ice cream is one of a kind. Blueberry cream layer with chunks of cranberry and black currant. Berry-licious!

info.name: Dry Fruit Overload Kulfi [AFGHAN]
info.description: Rich malai kulfi ice cream mixed with Afghan's premium pistas, almonds & cashews. A delightful blend!

info.name: Chocolate Hazelnut Chunks [TURKEY]
info.description: Extraordinary hazelnuts from Turkey mixed in rich & creamy chocolate ice cream. It's melt-in-the-mouth, it's nutty, it's irresistible!

info.name: Death By Chocolate [BELGIUM]
info.description: Finely crafted Belgian chocolate with choco-cookie chunks, white & dark chocolate chips & chocolate fudge sauce. This ice cream screams chocolate!

info.name: Red Velvet Cheesecake [SAN FRANCISCO]
info.description: Soft red velvet cake wrapped in smooth cream cheese, an ice cream that will give you the San Francisco feels!

info.name: Blueberry Cheesecake [GREECE]
info.description: Fresh, tarty blueberries smothered in fine Greek cheesecake. Silklike smooth and super creamy, this ice cream is like no other!

info.name: 100% Real Kesar Pista
info.description: Kashmir's 100% real saffron, premium pistachios & cashews. No artificial flavours. This ice cream is a royal feast!
